pageContext.claim: “[Democrats] want MS-13 to rule our country... Everyday, the brave men and women of ICE are liberating communities and towns from savage gangs like [MS-13] that are occupying our country like another nation would.”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats do not want the MS-13 gang to rule the country. MS-13 is active in prisons and in a few areas such as Los Angeles, Long Island and the D.C. region. Experts say Trump exaggerates the threat posed by the gang.
